author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
This is one of the most complex wooden cases Adam has yet to design and build: a traveling box to house and protect his animatronic Grogu while being as compact and portable as possible. It also needs to store the tools related to the puppet's operation and maintenance, as well as look beautiful as an illuminated display! Easy enough, right? 

Adam's animatronic Grogu project: https://youtu.be/KGhqvLLQFzY

Shot by Adam Savage and edited by Joey Fameli
Music by Jinglepunks
